               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380402-name-754" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-754" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-754" type="surname" value="PERKINS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-754" type="given" value="ALFRED"></interp>ALFRED PERKINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the umbrella business. On the 22nd of March I was in St. James's-park, about one o'clock—I was walking along with the crowd, and felt a slight pull at my pocket, and on looking round, I saw the prisoner wiping his mouth with my handkerchief—I was in the act of taking it from him, and the policeman reached over and took him—this handkerchief is mine—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380402-name-755" type="witnessName">
